77
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,320
And we understand that all scripture

78
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:40,119
is given by inspiration of God

79
00:02:40,119 --> 00:02:42,520
and God is using Paul to write back

80
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,320
to this church in Corinth.

81
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:46,740
And there's a group of people, false teachers,

82
00:02:46,740 --> 00:02:48,279
that are called the Judaizers.

83
00:02:48,279 --> 00:02:50,839
And these Judaizers had influenced

84
00:02:50,839 --> 00:02:52,880
the believers at Corinth.

85
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:56,520
