88
00:03:00,220 --> 00:03:01,720
because there were other factors as well,

89
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,160
but led to some of the friction

90
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:06,160
between the believers at the church in Corinth

91
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,639
